1)  The user will have the files that have been modified, sorted by extension, with
    some information displayed on how to deal with these modifications. (malicious or bit rot)
2)  The user can specify files to be encrypted and stored on the Google Drive.
3)  The user can sort the files, like last modified date, to see irregularities that may be malicious. (Im working on incorporating this in the GUI)
4)  Possibility of setting an event timer, such that the program would launch and do an update at specified intervals
5)  Run in background mode, icon in notification area with realtime monitoring